v12

## Changes

* Adds support for Nix 2.7.0

* Changes default Nix version from 2.6.1 to 2.7.0

* Removes support for Nix 2.7pre20220127_558c4ee

## Known issues

* `macos-latest` not currently not supported, use `macos-10.15` instead.
  See https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/issues/7
